com.cubeia.firebase.api.server.conf
Annotation Type Property

@Inherited
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Property

Annotation for method level configuration interfaces. This annotation can be used to override the class level inheritance policy, it can override the property name and it can set an optional default value.

Author:
lars.nilsson
